Bagaimana kabarnya, dokter?

50
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,000
Untungnya, dia dibawa tepat waktu.

51
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,360
Operasinya sangat sukses.

52
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,519
Begitu pasien bangun,

53
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,800
